Standard Poor's Corp affirm rating W.R. Grace Co's 575 mln dlrs debt follow fourth-quarter 1986 loss 560 mln dlrs. Affirmed company's BBB-minus senior debt BB-plus subordinate debt A-3 commercial paper. S P point fourth-quarter loss result write-off nearly 600 mln dlrs asset especially agricultural chemical natural resources. Because write-off effect Grace's cash S P affirm current rating note Grace intend sell agricultural business. Proceeds sale agricultural segment reduce Grace's debt Standard Poor's said. However S P clear whether Grace extricate project debt phosphate mining joint venture Four Corners. Despite today's rating affirmation S P caution Grace greater-than-usual vulnerability rating change two. "Uncertainty abounds firm's future ownership management direction" rating agency said. Reuter 